  "detailed_description": "This artistic floral arrangement game allows you to experience the subtle changes in your inner feelings while  adjusting the shapes and colors.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/960140/extras/a93635f3b13eb3b31a8eff37870c03ae.avif?t=1645625895\" width=616 height=376 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2>1, A variety of flowers and plants.<br><br>2, The shapes and colors of the plants are freely adjustable.<br>3, Display your work as a calendar every day.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Algorithmic Art</h2>For years I have been trying to generate natural objects using algorithms:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/960140/extras/3dc80e9df6d87ff3ec3aca96811dcbd4.avif?t=1645625895\" width=614 height=344 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/960140/extras/1aef85141a7c492deae7c28d864affcd.avif?t=1645625895\" width=610 height=344 /></span><br><br>However, the best display medium is still an independent game, I hope to get everyone's support!<br>Thank you for reading and watching. Hope you enjoy this game.",
  "about_the_game": "This artistic floral arrangement game allows you to experience the subtle changes in your inner feelings while  adjusting the shapes and colors.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/960140/extras/a93635f3b13eb3b31a8eff37870c03ae.avif?t=1645625895\" width=616 height=376 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2>1, A variety of flowers and plants.<br><br>2, The shapes and colors of the plants are freely adjustable.<br>3, Display your work as a calendar every day.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Algorithmic Art</h2>For years I have been trying to generate natural objects using algorithms:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/960140/extras/3dc80e9df6d87ff3ec3aca96811dcbd4.avif?t=1645625895\" width=614 height=344 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/960140/extras/1aef85141a7c492deae7c28d864affcd.avif?t=1645625895\" width=610 height=344 /></span><br><br>However, the best display medium is still an independent game, I hope to get everyone's support!<br>Thank you for reading and watching. Hope you enjoy this game.",
